    "slug": "my-teacher-told-my-mum-i-think-william-has-dyspraxia-and-mum-asked-what-that",
    "texto": "My teacher told my mum, 'I think William has dyspraxia,' and Mum asked what that meant. She said, 'Well, if I put a chair in the middle of the room and asked every child in the class to walk around it, William would be the only child in the class to walk into it.' Mum was like, 'Yeah, that's my boy'.",
